    <h1>Social Media Dashboard</h1>
    <p class="description">A centralised interface that aggregates performance metrics from multiple social platforms — followers, reach, engagement, and content performance — into <strong>one unified view</strong>, so teams can monitor, analyse, and report without jumping between native tools.</p>
