              <tr><td><strong>Hootsuite</strong></td><td>Large teams, many accounts</td><td>Broad platform support, strong team collaboration</td></tr>
              <tr><td><strong>Buffer</strong></td><td>Small teams, simple needs</td><td>Clean interface, affordable, easy to start</td></tr>
              <tr><td><strong>Databox</strong></td><td>Data-driven marketing teams</td><td>Connects social + CRM + ads + web analytics in one board</td></tr>
