            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>The best tool depends on your use case. Sprout Social is best for teams that need strong inbox + analytics in one tool. Hootsuite is best for large teams managing many accounts. Buffer is the simplest option for smaller teams focused on publishing. Databox and Google Looker Studio are best for custom reporting that needs to combine social data with other business metrics.</p></div></div>
          </div>
